name: Magie Flores
description: Hi! I’m Magie, 24 years old and single. I have always winced at the thought of online dating… but in the name of open-mindedness, f*** it. After being thoroughly disappointed in the trashy local nightlife, I have come to the conclusion that meeting people here might not be the worst idea. So, here goes… Hmm, there’s really not much to say here, i just want to live life to the fullest. For now I’m looking for someone to hookup with, who isn’t a keyboard warrior and just all talk… if you’re what i’m looking for then send me a message.
